T02D3522:166a-1: kal pokta da sha bhu dza s'i ta m'a r'i tsyee s'a dha nam /
T02D3522:166a-3: rtog pa las gsungs pa'i 'od zer can dkar mo phyag bcu pa'i sgrub thabs /
T02D3522:166a-4: 'phags ma 'od zer can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3522:166a-5: sngon du gsungs pa'i cho gas pam yig las skyes
T02D3522:166a-6: pa'i sna tshogs padma'i steng du zla ba la mam
T02D3522:166a-7: yig dkar po las skyes pa'i 'od zer can dkar
T02D3522:166a-10: zhabs bzhi pa'i bdag nyid du skad cig gis bsam par bya'o //
T02D3522:166a-11: de la rtsa ba'i zhal dkar po /
T02D3522:166a-15: dbu'i steng du zhal ser mo /
T02D3522:166a-16: rin po che sna tshogs pa'i zur phud gsum gyis brgyan cing ral pa'i cod pan can /
T02D3522:166a-17: phyag g-yas pa lnga rnams na nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor dang /
T02D3522:166a-20: lcags kyu dang khab phyag na bsnams pa'o //
T02D3522:166a-21: g-yon pa lnga rnams na zla ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
T02D3522:166a-23: mya ngan med pa'i lo ma dang /
T02D3522:166a-24: zhags pa dang bcas pa'i sdigs mdzub dang /
T02D3522:166a-26: lang tsho gzhon zhing phu dung stod g-yogs dkar po can /
T02D3522:166a-27: mchod rten gyi nang na gnas pa /
T02D3522:166a-28: phag bdun gyi shing rta la zhon pa /
T02D3522:166a-32: tshangs pa rnams zhabs bzhis mnan pa /
T02D3522:166a-33: de'i shing rta'i dbus su gnas pa'i chu srin mnan pa'i bcom ldan 'das ma gzhan te /
T02D3522:166a-34: sku mdog nag mo phag gi gdong pa can /
T02D3522:166a-35: rdo rje dang sdigs mdzub ni g-yas dang g-yon gyi phyag na'o //
T02D3522:166a-36: g-yas phyogs su gzhan bcom ldan 'das ma ni phag
T02D3522:166a-37: zhal dmar mo phyag bzhi ba g-yas pa gnyis kyis
T02D3522:166a-38: lcags kyu dang khab bsnams pa'o //
T02D3522:166b-0: phyag @166b g-yon pa gnyis kyis zhags pa dang bcas pa'i sdigs mdzub dang skud pa bsnams pa'o //
T02D3522:166b-1: mdzes pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa'o //
T02D3522:166b-2: g-yon gyi phyogs su rje btsun ma gzhan rnams ni phag zhal dmar mo'o //
T02D3522:166b-3: rna ba'i bar du bskang ba'i gzhu dang mda' dang /
T02D3522:166b-5: mya ngan med pa'i shing gi yal ga ni g-yas dang g-yon gyi phyag na bsnams pa'o //
T02D3522:166b-6: sna tshogs pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa ste /
T02D3522:166b-7: shing rta 'dren pa'i phag gi 'og nas nyi ma la sogs pa'i gzugs gza' dgu ste /
T02D3522:166b-8: nyi mas nye bar 'tshe ba'i nad kyi tshogs kyang
T02D3522:166b-9: mi'i gzugs kyi 'og tu ltung bar bsam par bya'o
T02D3522:166b-10: // de nas snying ga'i zla ba la gnas pa'i
T02D3522:166b-11: mam gi sa bon gyi 'od zer gyis de bzhin
T02D3522:166b-12: gshegs pa rnams gdan drangs te /
T02D3522:166b-13: dbang bskur ba blangs nas dbu la rnam par snang mdzad kyis rgyas gdab pa'o //
T02D3522:166b-14: de nas snying ga'i sa bon las de bzhin du
T02D3522:166b-15: phreng ba'i rnam pa lta bu'i sngags kyi yi ge
T02D3522:166b-16: rnams kha nas 'thon nas lte ba /
T02D3522:166b-18: kha nas slar yang lte ba la sogs par 'khor
T02D3522:166b-19: lo 'khor ba'i rim pa bzhin du sngags bzlas par
T02D3522:166b-20: bya'o // de la sngags ni 'di yin te /
T02D3522:166b-21: aom m'a r'i tsyee m'am h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02D3522:166b-22: rang gi sa bon gyi byin gyis brlabs la zas
T02D3522:166b-23: la sogs pa thams cad la rjes su gnas par
T02D3522:166b-24: bya'o // ngal na yi ge brgya ba'i sngags brjod la ci bder gnas par bya'o //
